		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I think it would be a better idea to start from scratch using a more modern BBS system, however it's just a suggestion.
<br />
<br />Some of the threads have relevance but I think that at least 95% of them are no longer relevant. If someone asks a question and gets his answer back in 2007, there is no real value to this.
<br />
<br />Only a few threads about new discoveries about the hardware or things like that are actually relevant.

		

		</td>
