		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Starting from scratch is stupid.  The board should be easy enough to reconstruct on any flat-style board system, given the original unparsed plain text for each post, poster, subject, post time-date, and thread ID.  The only thing that might get lost is individual post subjects, which some board systems don't use.
<br />I also don't like the idea of a read-only archived board.

		

